# Square Design System

All frontend UI should follow Square's design language: clean, minimal, light-themed with strong typography and generous whitespace.

## Color Palette

### Primary
- **Square Blue**: `#006AFF` (CTAs, links, active states)
- **Blue Hover**: `#0056CC`
- **Blue Light**: `#E6F2FF` (subtle backgrounds, focus rings)

### Neutrals
- **Black**: `#1A1A1A` (headings)
- **Dark Gray**: `#4A4A4A` (body text)
- **Medium Gray**: `#8A8A8A` (secondary text, placeholders)
- **Border Gray**: `#E5E5E5` (borders, dividers)
- **Background**: `#F6F6F6` (subtle section backgrounds)
- **White**: `#FFFFFF` (primary background, cards)

### Status
- **Success**: `#00D632` (green accents, positive scores)
- **Warning**: `#FF9500` (amber alerts)
- **Danger**: `#E02B1D` (errors, critical issues)
- **Info**: `#006AFF` (same as primary blue)

## Typography
- **Font stack**: `"Square Sans", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif`
- Headings: **700** weight, `#1A1A1A`
- Body: **400** weight, `#4A4A4A`
- Small/labels: **500** weight, `#8A8A8A`

## Components

### Buttons
- **Primary**: `bg-[#006AFF] text-white rounded-full px-6 py-3 font-semibold hover:bg-[#0056CC]`
- **Secondary**: `bg-white text-[#006AFF] border-2 border-[#006AFF] rounded-full px-6 py-3 font-semibold`
- **Ghost**: `text-[#4A4A4A] hover:bg-[#F6F6F6] rounded-lg px-4 py-2`
- Always pill-shaped (rounded-full) for primary/secondary CTAs

### Cards
- `bg-white rounded-2xl border border-[#E5E5E5] p-6 shadow-sm`
- Hover: `shadow-md -translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200`

### Inputs
- `bg-white border border-[#E5E5E5] rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-[#1A1A1A]`
- Focus: `border-[#006AFF] ring-2 ring-[#006AFF]/10`
- Placeholder: `text-[#8A8A8A]`

### Tables
- Header: `bg-[#F6F6F6] text-[#8A8A8A] text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-medium`
- Rows: `border-b border-[#E5E5E5] hover:bg-[#F6F6F6]/50`
- Text: `text-[#1A1A1A]` for primary, `text-[#4A4A4A]` for secondary

### Navigation
- Sidebar: `bg-white border-r border-[#E5E5E5]`
- Active link: `bg-[#E6F2FF] text-[#006AFF] font-medium border-l-2 border-[#006AFF]`
- Inactive: `text-[#4A4A4A] hover:bg-[#F6F6F6]`

## Spacing
- 8px grid system. Use Tailwind: `p-2` (8px), `p-4` (16px), `p-6` (24px), `p-8` (32px)
- Section gaps: `space-y-8` or `gap-8`
- Card padding: `p-6` minimum

## Borders & Radius
- Small: `rounded-lg` (8px) — inputs, small cards
- Medium: `rounded-xl` (12px) — cards
- Large: `rounded-2xl` (16px) — feature cards
- Buttons: `rounded-full` (pill)

## Shadows
- Subtle: `shadow-sm` (cards at rest)
- Elevated: `shadow-md` (card hover, dropdowns)
- Modal: `shadow-xl`

## Score Colors (for grading/analytics UIs)
- Excellent (>=90): `text-[#00D632]` with `bg-[#00D632]/10`
- Good (>=80): `text-[#006AFF]` with `bg-[#006AFF]/10`
- Fair (>=70): `text-[#FF9500]` with `bg-[#FF9500]/10`
- Needs Work (<70): `text-[#E02B1D]` with `bg-[#E02B1D]/10`

## Chart Colors
- Primary: `#006AFF`
- Secondary: `#00D632`
- Tertiary: `#FF9500`
- Quaternary: `#E02B1D`
- Fifth: `#8B5CF6`
- Grid/axis: `#E5E5E5`, tick labels `#8A8A8A`
